---
title: Sweet Pepper, Chicken Breasts and Black Bean Taquitos with Monterey Jack Cheese and Fresh Salad
description: Nutritious and delicious black beans take centre stage in this fun Mexican-inspired recipe. Cooked with sweet onions, peppers and zesty chipotle sauce, everything is then wrapped and baked with stretchy Monterey Jack cheese for ultimate cheese pull satisfaction!
